{"reactions":{"fire":1,"laugh":0},"_id":"69dc77f8db07f79da63f843b","title":"A new couple","content":"Rashmika-Vijay wedding live: Key Kodava wedding rituals\nOne of the key distinctions of a Kodava wedding is its simplicity. Unlike many Hindu ceremonies, it does not centre around the sacred fire or elaborate pheras conducted by priests. Instead, the rituals are intimate and led by family elders, with an emphasis on symbolic acts, blessings and cultural identity rather than priest-led chants or mantras.\n\nRather than elaborate feasts or ritual-heavy ceremonies, Kodava weddings are marked by vibrant folk traditions. The celebrations come alive with the rhythmic beats of Valaga drums, traditional warrior dances and community songs. In the past, ceremonial gun salutes were also a part of the festivities, though these are now largely scaled down.Rashmika Mandanna and Vijay Deverakonda had their traditional Telugu wedding ceremony this morning at 10:10 AM. The second ceremony took place in the evening to honour Rashmika Mandanna's Kodava heritage.\n\nTheir official wedding pictures are now finally out!\n\nRashmika Mandanna wrote a long note sharing pictures from their wedding ceremonies, \"Hi my loves, Introducing to you now My Husband! Mr. Vijay Deverakonda!! The man who taught me what true love feels like, The man who showed me what being in peace feels like! The man who told me everyday that dreaming big was absolutely ok and constantly telling me I was capable of achieving something much more than what I could possibly think I ever could!\"\n\nShe added, \"The man who's never stopped me from dancing like no one's watching..the man who showed me travelling with friends is the best thing ever, and trust me I could write a book on this man!\" ","tags":["#wedding #vijay #rashmika"],"image":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","author":"TestUser","likes":0,"dislikes":0,"upvoters":[],"downvoters":[],"spamScore":0,"status":"under review","isPinned":false,"comments":[],"reactedUsers":["keerthana"],"hasReport":true,"timestamp":"2026-04-13T04:58:32.228Z","__v":0,"reportReason":"Spam test","reporter":"admin"}